---
title: Cranberry Apple Pork Chops with Asparagus and Herbed Potatoes
description: Apples, cranberries, asparagus, potatoes, onion, and parsley: that’s not a shopping list for your next trip to the produce market. It’s all the fruit and veg bounty that’s in this recipe. So you can rest assured that your family will get their fill of their five-a-day with this dinner, plus a hearty serving of protein from the succulent, sauce-drizzled pork chops.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cranberry-apple-pork-chops-8b3af460.jpg
